        2. Promise's Role in TML -> Goal: Show Relationships -> Method: HTML/CSS Flexbox Diagram -> Interaction: Hover effects to highlight connections. Justification: Visually clarifies the abstract architectural connections between TML pillars, making the system's logic easier to grasp. Method: HTML/CSS.
        3. Promise's Impact -> Goal: Compare & Persuade -> Method: Interactive Radar Chart -> Interaction: Toggle buttons to switch between 'Legacy AI' and 'TML AI' datasets. Justification: Offers a stark, quantitative visualization of the security and integrity improvements the Promise provides, making a compelling case for its necessity. Method: Chart.js.
